      ]
    }
  ]
}
Error Response: If the item creation fails, the API returns specific error messages. Below are two examples of potential errors:
Example 1 - Duplicate Item:

{
  "Message": "The Item entered already exists.",
  "Success": false,
  "RefreshItems": null
}
Example 2 - Null Item:

{
  "Message": "The item entered cannot be null in item_mst.  INSERT rolled back.",
  "Success": false,
  "RefreshItems": null
}
NOTE: Error responses may vary depending on the validation rules or constraints violated during the item creation process. The Message field will contain details about the specific issue.
